text: Margny is the name or part of the name of several communes in France: * Margny, in the Ardennes département * Margny, in the Marne département * Margny-aux-Cerises, in the Oise département * Margny-lès-Compiègne, in the Oise département * Margny-sur-Matz, in the Oise département
title: Margny
